| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2084 — Recovery Inhibition (spacebears)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 40fa0c63-5aee-5f87-9466-f3afa83cfd08"
